        amongst other things. Find many more interesting facts in my <a href="/cv">curriculum vitae</a>.</p>
    <p>I think the only excuse to not be learning is because you're dead (and even then I'm not positive). As such, I
        spend a lot of time <a href='/reading'>reading</a>.</p>
    <p>While I crave movement, San Francisco is where I'm most often found. Prior to there, home has been Vancouver,
